mod groxide_test_api

A test fixture crate exercising all Rust item kinds for groxide testing.

This crate exists solely to produce rustdoc JSON that covers every item kind
groxide needs to handle: structs, enums, traits, functions, constants, type aliases,
macros, statics, unions, re-exports, nested modules, and more.

Modules:
  containers                      Container types for testing module-level items.
  deeply                          A module for testing deeply nested paths.
  reexports                       Module for testing re-export handling.
  traits                          Trait definitions for testing trait rendering.

Structs:
  GenericStruct                   A generic container holding a single value.
  SimpleStruct                    A simple struct with no generics.
  UnstableStruct                  A feature-gated struct.

Enums:
  Direction                       An enum representing cardinal directions.
  Shape                           An enum with data-carrying variants.

Unions:
  IntOrFloat                      A union for testing union item rendering.

# Safety

Accessing union fields requires `unsafe` since the compiler cannot guarantee
which field was last written.

Functions:
  pub fn add(a: i32, b: i32) -> i32                           Adds two numbers together.
  pub fn generic_fn<T: std::fmt::Display, U: Into<String>>(value: T, _label: U) -> String  A function with multiple generic parameters.
  pub fn unicode_docs() -> &'static str                       A function demonstrating unicode in documentation.
  pub fn unstable_api() -> &'static str                       An item only available with the `unstable` feature.

Type Aliases:
  pub type Callback = fn(i32) -> bool                         A type alias for a callback function.
  pub type Result<T> = std::result::Result<T, String>         A type alias for results in this crate.

Constants:
  pub const DEFAULT_GREETING: &str                            The default greeting string.
  pub const MAX_BUFFER_SIZE: usize                            The maximum buffer size in bytes.

Statics:
  pub static GLOBAL_COUNTER: std::sync::atomic::AtomicUsize   A global counter for testing static items.
  pub static VERSION: &str                                    A simple static string.

Macros:
  greet                           Generates a greeting string.
